snippet.title: Urbex Murder - Gameplay Preview | Urbex Horror Soon on Steam
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3282980/Urbex_Murder/

Urbex Murder is a horror game set in abandoned urban locations. Play solo or with up to four friends in co-op mode to survive the threats hiding in the dark. Explore dark and dangerous areas, where each map offers unique events and scary encounters based on the setting. A demo is coming soon on Steam! For more information, visit our website.

Learn more:
Web site: https://www.rantabl.com/
X: https://twitter.com/Rantabl_3d
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/rantabl-com-523316199992590358
